description: This dashboard servers the purpose for monitoring reliability executions.

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  start_time AS "time",
  build_details AS metric,
  id
FROM run
WHERE
  id = $RunID
ORDER BY 1,2

SELECT
  start_time AS "time",
  release AS metric,
  id
FROM run
WHERE
  id = $RunID
ORDER BY 1,2

SELECT
  start_time AS "time",
  description AS metric,
  id
FROM run
WHERE
  id = $RunID
ORDER BY 1,2

SELECT
  start_time AS "time",
  run_type AS metric,
  id
FROM run
WHERE
  id = $RunID
ORDER BY 1,2

SELECT
  start_time AS "time",
  name AS metric,
  id
FROM run
WHERE
  id = $RunID
ORDER BY 1,2

SELECT
  start_time AS "time",
  run_status AS metric,
  id
FROM run
WHERE
  id = $RunID
ORDER BY 1,2

SELECT
  start_time AS "time",
  environment AS metric,
  id
FROM run
WHERE
  id = $RunID
ORDER BY 1,2

SELECT
  end_time AS "time",
  id
FROM iteration
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(end_time) AND
  run_id = $RunID
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  end_time AS "time",
  status AS metric,
  iteration_number
FROM iteration
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(end_time) AND
  status = 'COMPLETED' AND
  run_id = $RunID
ORDER BY 1,2

SELECT
  end_time AS "time",
  status AS metric,
  iteration_number
FROM iteration
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(end_time) AND
  status = 'FAILED' AND
  run_id = $RunID
ORDER BY 1,2

SELECT
  start_time AS "time",
  status AS metric,
  iteration_number
FROM iteration
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(start_time) AND
  run_id = $RunID
ORDER BY 1,2

SELECT
  start_time AS "time",
  status AS metric,
  iteration_number
FROM iteration
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(start_time) AND
  run_id = $RunID
ORDER BY 1,2

SELECT
  start_time AS "time",
  status AS metric,
  $LockID
FROM iteration
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(start_time) AND
  run_id = $RunID
ORDER BY 1,2

SELECT
  start_time AS "time",
  status AS metric,
  iteration_number
FROM iteration
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(start_time) AND
  status = 'FAILED' AND
  run_id = $RunID
ORDER BY 1,2

SELECT
  time_of_occurance AS "time",
  incident_type AS metric,
  iteration_id
FROM incident
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time_of_occurance) AND
  run_id = $RunID
ORDER BY 1,2

SELECT
  time_of_occurance AS "time",
  incident_type AS metric,
  $LockID
FROM incident
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time_of_occurance) AND
  run_id = $RunID
ORDER BY 1,2

SELECT
  time_of_occurance AS "time",
  message AS metric,
  iteration_id
FROM incident
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time_of_occurance) AND
  run_id = $RunID
ORDER BY 1,2
